  "title": "MemTrace Platform Overview",
  "content": {
    "type": "factual",
    "format": "markdown",
    "body": "MemTrace is an open platform designed for building shared knowledge through minimal, well-connected Memory Nodes. Its core design goal is to allow any human or AI agent to reach any answer by following the shortest possible path through a graph of small, typed relationships — rather than reading through large documents."
